	(313, '전주 한옥마을 후기!!', '<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 2; font-family: &quot;Nanum Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"><table cellspacing="1" cellpadding="2" width="99%" bgcolor="#ffffff"><tbody><tr><td bgcolor="#df5916" width="350" style="margin: 0px; border: 1px solid rgb(223, 89, 22); line-height: 2; height: 29px;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"></span><p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; line-height: 1;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-weight: 700;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;전주 전동성당</span></span></span></p></td><td style="margin: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(255, 255, 255) rgb(255, 255, 255) rgb(223, 89, 22); border-image: initial; line-height: 2; height: 29px;"></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-family: &quot;Nanum Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"></p><p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-family: &quot;Nanum Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 2; text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;"><span class="imageblock" style="margin: 5px 0px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; width: 400px; line-height: 2; font-size: 9pt; height: auto;"><img srcset="https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&amp;fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile29.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F25671F485623B26509280C" src="https://t1.daumcdn.net/cfile/tistory/25671F485623B26509" width="400" height="602" filename="20151017-012.jpg" filemime="image/jpeg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; height: auto; max-width: 100%;"></span><span class="imageblock" style="margin: 5px 0px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; width: 400px; line-height: 2; font-size: 9pt; height: auto;"><img srcset="https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&amp;fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile30.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F24399F485623B2673AD0B6" src="https://t1.daumcdn.net/cfile/tistory/24399F485623B2673A" width="400" height="602" filename="20151017-011.jpg" filemime="image/jpeg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; height: auto; max-width: 100%;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-family: &quot;Nanum Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; clear: none; float: none;"><span style="line-height: 32px;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">우선은 전주 한옥마을에서 유명한&nbsp;</span><span style="font-weight: 700;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">전주전동성당</span></span></span><span style="line-height: 32px;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">&lt;</span></span><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 32px;">사적 제288호 (1981년 9월 25일 지정)&gt;</span><span style="line-height: 32px;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">에 들렀다.</span></span><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 32px;">&nbsp;외관이 이국적이고 영화 "약속"의 촬영지로 사용 되면서 유명해져서&nbsp;사람들이 사진을 관광을 많이 오지만, 이 곳은&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 32px;">1801년에</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 32px;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 32px;">천주교도들이 박해 받고 처형된 곳이다. 이들의 순교를 기리기 위해서 1891년에 프랑스 보두네 신부가 부지를 매입하고 1908년에 착공하고&nbsp;1914년 완공한 성당이다.&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-family: &quot;Nanum Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 32px;">&nbsp;</span><span class="imageblock" style="margin: 5px 0px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; width: 400px; font-size: 9pt; line-height: 24px; height: auto;"><img srcset="https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&amp;fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile28.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F2761D3485623B26E0F0B6D" src="https://t1.daumcdn.net/cfile/tistory/2761D3485623B26E0F" width="400" height="602" filename="20151017-019.jpg" filemime="image/jpeg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; height: auto; max-width: 100%;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-family: &quot;Nanum Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 32px;">중앙과 좌우에 종탑이 있는데, 내가 머무르는 동안은 울리지는 않았다.(아예 울리지 않는 것인지도 모르겠다.) 붉은&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 32px;">벽돌로 쌓아진&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 32px;">외관은 정말 아름다워서 한참을 바라봤다. 참 좋아하는 색감의 건물이었다.</span></p><p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-family: &quot;Nanum Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;"><span class="imageblock" style="margin: 5px 0px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; width: 720px; line-height: 24px; height: auto;"><img srcset="https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&amp;fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile23.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F234B8B485623B26B282B6F" src="https://t1.daumcdn.net/cfile/tistory/234B8B485623B26B28" width="720" height="479" filename="20151017-017.jpg" filemime="image/jpeg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; height: auto; max-width: 100%;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-family: &quot;Nanum Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 2; text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;"><span class="imageblock" style="margin: 5px 0px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; width: 720px; height: auto;"><img srcset="https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&amp;fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile30.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F234DFE485623B269256470" src="https://t1.daumcdn.net/cfile/tistory/234DFE485623B26925" width="720" height="479" filename="20151017-014.jpg" filemime="image/jpeg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; height: auto; max-width: 100%;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-family: &quot;Nanum Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 2; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 32px;">내부는 출입할 수 없었지만, 아치형으로 만들어져서 외관못지 않게 아름다웠다.</span></p>', 'Rona